[ GASPS ]
FUCK.

39:38.477 --> 39:39.509
OH, MY GOD!

39:39.511 --> 39:40.910
[ PANTING ]
KEEP IT DOWN.

39:40.912 --> 39:42.545
I'M TRYING TO SLEEP.

39:42.547 --> 39:44.080
I'M...

39:44.082 --> 39:46.583
[ GASPING ]

39:46.585 --> 39:48.385
I'M...

39:59.230 --> 40:01.164
[ CLOCK TICKING ]

40:02.433 --> 40:05.502
OH, WE REALLY ARE GLAD
YOU GUYS STOPPED BY.

40:05.504 --> 40:07.704
MASON? MASON, BABY,
SLOW DOWN, BABY.

40:07.706 --> 40:09.873
BUDDY, DON'T TRIP.
YOU'RE GONNA FALL.

40:09.875 --> 40:11.341
[ CHUCKLES ]

40:11.343 --> 40:13.943
WELL, WE WERE REALLY
GLAD TO HEAR FROM YOU.

40:13.945 --> 40:17.213
YOU KNOW, WE TRIED
TO CALL SEVERAL TIMES,

40:17.215 --> 40:19.015
BUT THERE WAS
NEVER ANY ANSWER.

40:19.017 --> 40:20.517
THINK SHE NEVER
HEARD OF EMAIL.

40:20.519 --> 40:21.551
[ LAUGHS ]
SHUT UP.

40:21.553 --> 40:23.553
[ CHUCKLES ]

40:23.555 --> 40:26.523
HEY, ARE YOU GUYS OKAY?

40:28.058 --> 40:29.259
MICHAEL?

40:29.261 --> 40:30.927
YEAH, WE'RE FINE.

40:30.929 --> 40:32.862
MICHAEL'S JUST
BEEN REALLY BUSY

40:32.864 --> 40:34.464
WITH HIS--
WITH HIS BOOK.

40:34.466 --> 40:35.532
GOOD.

40:35.534 --> 40:36.900
YEAH, YEAH.
THAT'S GOOD.

40:36.902 --> 40:39.035
WE ALL GO THROUGH TIMES
LIKE THIS, RIGHT?

40:39.037 --> 40:41.871
I MEAN, LAST YEAR,
I WAS A BIG BALL OF STRESS

40:41.873 --> 40:43.239
WHEN UPS CUT BACK
MY SHIFTS,

40:43.241 --> 40:47.310
YOU KNOW,
BUT WE PULLED THROUGH.

40:47.312 --> 40:49.546
BAD TIMES ARE LIKE
GOOD TIMES, RIGHT?

40:49.548 --> 40:50.780
THEY EVENTUALLY END.

40:50.782 --> 40:53.249
YEAH, I'VE JUST
BEEN SO EXHAUSTED

40:53.251 --> 40:55.485
WITH THE OPENING
OF THE BOUTIQUE,

40:55.487 --> 41:00.657
AND THE PHONE'S JUST BEEN
RINGING NONSTOP.

41:00.659 --> 41:02.158
FROM WHOM?

41:02.160 --> 41:04.427
JUST
DIFFERENT PEOPLE.

41:04.429 --> 41:06.763
WE--WE TALKED TO THE
POLICE ABOUT IT,

41:06.765 --> 41:07.997
AND THEY'VE FINALLY AGREED
TO TRACE THE CALLS.

41:07.999 --> 41:09.766
THAT'S GOOD.

41:09.768 --> 41:12.068
BET IT'LL FEEL GOOD WHEN THEY
CATCH THE PUNKS, HUH?

41:12.070 --> 41:13.803
THEY BETTER HOPE
THE POLICE GET 'EM FIRST,

41:13.805 --> 41:15.605
'CAUSE IF I DO,
I'M GONNA CUT OFF

41:15.607 --> 41:17.106
EACH OF THEIR FINGERS ONE BY ONE
WITH PINKING SHEARS

41:17.108 --> 41:18.575
UNTIL THEY CAN NEVER DIAL A
FUCKING PHONE AGAIN.

41:22.947 --> 41:25.415
WELL, LET'S HOPE
IT DOESN'T COME TO THAT.

41:25.417 --> 41:26.683
[ CHUCKLES ]

41:26.685 --> 41:29.486
THE GOOD THING IS,
IS THAT NOBODY GOT HURT.

41:29.488 --> 41:32.455
I'M SURE THAT THE POLICE ARE
GONNA GET TO THE BOTTOM OF IT.

41:32.457 --> 41:34.457
[ RECORDING PLAYING ]
[ MASON GIGGLING ]

41:34.459 --> 41:35.492
[ BEEP ]

41:35.494 --> 41:37.527
[ GARBLED MESSAGE PLAYING ]

41:39.530 --> 41:40.530
[ BEEP ]

41:42.533 --> 41:44.434
[ BEEP ]

41:44.436 --> 41:45.768
[ LAUGHING ]
...AH-SHING-TUN.

41:47.538 --> 41:50.206
WAIT. STOP.

41:50.208 --> 41:51.207
[ GARBLED MESSAGE
PLAYING ]

41:51.209 --> 41:53.810
MASON. MASON.

41:53.812 --> 41:56.679
MASON, STOP!

41:56.681 --> 41:58.481
[ CRYING ]

41:58.483 --> 42:00.617
[ GARBLED MESSAGE
PLAYING ]

42:00.619 --> 42:02.652
VA-LA-REE
WA-SHING-TUN.

42:02.654 --> 42:04.153
MASON, HONEY,
WHAT HAPPENED?!

42:04.155 --> 42:05.955
[ CRYING ]
MICHAEL, WHAT HAPPENED?

42:05.957 --> 42:07.724
MICHAEL!

42:07.726 --> 42:09.792
MY GOD. COME ON, BABY.

42:09.794 --> 42:11.694
COME ON. COME ON,
GET UP. GET UP.

42:11.696 --> 42:13.496
BILL!

42:13.498 --> 42:15.398
VA-LA-REE WA-SHING-TUN.

42:15.400 --> 42:16.699
BILL: WHAT?

42:16.701 --> 42:18.301
DID YOU PUSH MASON?

42:18.303 --> 42:20.803
HEY, WHAT'D YOU
DO TO MY KID?

42:20.805 --> 42:22.071
ARE YOU LISTENING?!

42:22.073 --> 42:23.106
WHAT IS WRONG WITH--

42:28.846 --> 42:30.513
MICHAEL,
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?!

42:30.515 --> 42:31.714
MICHAEL, STOP IT!

42:31.716 --> 42:33.716
STOP IT, MICHAEL!
STOP!

42:33.718 --> 42:35.585
[ BILL GASPING ]

42:35.587 --> 42:37.420
BILL.

42:37.422 --> 42:39.255
OH, MY GOD!
GET THE FUCK OFF OF HIM!

42:39.257 --> 42:40.723
BILL, I'M SORRY, MAN.
DON'T TOUCH HIM!

42:40.725 --> 42:41.724
GET OFF! GET OFF!

42:41.726 --> 42:43.860
GOD, YOU GUYS!

42:43.862 --> 42:45.228
ARE YOU OKAY?
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

42:45.230 --> 42:48.064
MICHAEL, WHAT THE FUCK
IS WRONG WITH YOU?!

42:48.066 --> 42:49.999
I'M SORRY.

42:50.001 --> 42:51.668
I CAN'T FUCKING
BELIEVE YOU.

42:51.670 --> 42:53.703
LET'S GO.
WE GOTTA GET OUT OF HERE.

42:53.705 --> 42:55.738
LET'S GET MASON.
LET'S GET OUTTA HERE.

42:55.740 --> 42:57.106
KATHERINE:
MARY, PLEASE, I--

42:57.108 --> 42:58.207
KAT, I CANNOT--

42:58.209 --> 42:59.742
I'M SORRY.

43:04.548 --> 43:05.848
I PLAYED
THE MESSAGE BACKWARDS,

43:05.850 --> 43:07.517
AND THAT'S WHAT I HEARD.

43:07.519 --> 43:09.252
YEAH, I PLAYED
THE MESSAGE BACKWARDS.

43:09.254 --> 43:10.787
YEAH, I KNOW
IT SOUNDS CRAZY,

43:10.789 --> 43:12.355
BUT YOU GOTTA
LISTEN TO ME!

43:12.357 --> 43:13.856
I PLAYED
THE MESSAGE BACKWARDS.

43:13.858 --> 43:14.958
I HEARD THE--

43:14.960 --> 43:18.261
HELLO? YES,
I'M SORRY, SHERIFF.

43:18.263 --> 43:20.630
IT'S JUST HE HASN'T
BEEN FEELING GOOD.

43:20.632 --> 43:22.699
CAN YOU PLEASE
JUST LET US KNOW

43:22.701 --> 43:24.067
IF YOU FIND OUT
ANYTHING? THANKS.

43:24.069 --> 43:25.735
WHAT DID HE SAY?
ENOUGH!

43:25.737 --> 43:27.704
YOU'RE PUSHING EVERYONE AWAY,
INCLUDING ME!

43:27.706 --> 43:29.105
NO, BABY! NO, LISTEN!

43:29.107 --> 43:30.707
YOU SAID THAT YOU
WOULD ALWAYS BELIEVE ME

43:30.709 --> 43:32.275
AS LONG AS I TOLD YOU
THE TRUTH!

43:32.277 --> 43:35.144
AND I'M TELLING YOU
I NEED YOU TO BELIEVE ME NOW!

43:35.146 --> 43:37.080
I--I HEARD SOMETHING
ON THE MACHINE,

43:37.082 --> 43:39.082
OKAY?
WILL YOU JUST LISTEN?

43:39.084 --> 43:40.450
NO NEW MESSAGES.
THERE'S A--

43:40.452 --> 43:42.585
NO NEW MESSAGES.
THE, UH--

43:42.587 --> 43:44.787
NO NEW MESSAGES.
NO NEW MESSAGES...

43:44.789 --> 43:47.123
YES, I KNOW I--
NO NEW MESSAGES.

43:47.125 --> 43:48.324
I KNOW
I HEARD SOMETHING.

43:48.326 --> 43:51.494
NO NEW MESSAGES.
NO--NO NEW MESSAGES.

43:51.496 --> 43:55.798
W-W-WHEN YOU
PLAY IT BACKWARDS...

43:56.967 --> 43:59.235
IT--SHE WAS--

44:00.270 --> 44:01.638
IT WA--

44:01.640 --> 44:03.573
SHE SAID HER NAME
WAS VALERIE WASHINGTON.

44:03.575 --> 44:05.341
DO--

44:05.343 --> 44:07.944
DO WE KNOW
A VALERIE WASHINGTON?

44:07.946 --> 44:09.479
NO, WE DON'T KNOW
ANY VALERIE!

44:09.481 --> 44:11.414
WE DON'T KNOW ANY
VALERIE WASHINGTON!

44:11.416 --> 44:12.849
YOU DIDN'T
HEAR ANYTHING!

44:16.453 --> 44:18.187
HONEY...

44:18.189 --> 44:19.922
YOU GOTTA TRUST ME.

44:21.425 --> 44:24.394
I THINK YOU NEED TO TAKE
A BREAK FROM YOUR BOOK.

44:25.696 --> 44:28.231
I THINK THE PRESSURE'S
GETTING TO YOU.

44:35.272 --> 44:36.272
IT'S OKAY.

45:20.684 --> 45:24.387
NOW, MY REASONS FOR DRINKING
WERE ALMOST OCCUPATIONAL.

45:24.389 --> 45:26.022
I WAS A PSYCHIATRIST.
AND BEING A PSYCHIATRIST,

45:26.024 --> 45:27.724
I LISTENED
TO PEOPLE'S PROBLEMS

45:27.726 --> 45:30.927
ALL THE TIME EVERY DAY ALL--YOU
KNOW, ON TOP OF MY OWN.

45:30.929 --> 45:32.562
THEN OF COURSE,
MY ALCOHOLISM.

45:32.564 --> 45:36.365
ALL I--I FELT
THAT DRINKING WAS, UM,

45:36.367 --> 45:37.834
MY ESCAPE,

45:37.836 --> 45:39.902
UM, THAT I DESERVED IT.

45:41.071 --> 45:44.307
AND SO
I STARTED TO DRINK.

45:45.843 --> 45:47.009
AND...

45:48.746 --> 45:51.447
I GOT LOST.

45:51.449 --> 45:52.949
I GOT VERY LOST,

45:52.951 --> 45:55.051
AND I LOST MANY THINGS.

45:55.053 --> 45:56.586
I LOST EVERYTHING.

45:56.588 --> 45:59.122
I LOST MY JOB,

45:59.124 --> 46:01.524
LOST MY WIFE.

46:04.294 --> 46:06.929
I LOST MY REPUTATION.

46:06.931 --> 46:09.432
I LOST MY DIGNITY.

46:09.434 --> 46:12.635
I WAS HUMILIATED BEYOND
ANY REASONABLE MEASURE.

46:14.037 --> 46:15.972
I LOST MY KIDS.

46:18.275 --> 46:20.476
DID THAT STOP ME? NO.

46:22.379 --> 46:24.380
SEE, I COULDN'T
ACCEPT THE FACT

46:24.382 --> 46:28.117
THAT I LOVED THE NEXT DRINK MORE
THAN I LOVED MY OWN CHILDREN.

46:29.419 --> 46:31.687
BUT I DID...

46:32.923 --> 46:34.657
THEN.

46:34.659 --> 46:37.760
AND WE ALL KNOW THAT GETTING
SOBER IS JUST HALF THE BATTLE.

46:37.762 --> 46:41.597
IT'S STAYING SOBER,
STAYING SOBER.

46:41.599 --> 46:43.499
LADIES AND GENTLEMEN, STAYING
SOBER IS THE HARDEST THING.

46:43.501 --> 46:45.635
IT'S THE HARDEST PART,

46:45.637 --> 46:47.303
AND IT'S THE HARDEST THING I'VE
EVER DONE, AND IT IS

46:47.305 --> 46:50.473
WE CAN ALL COME UP WITH AN
EXCUSE TO HAVE A DRINK,

46:50.475 --> 46:51.240
FOR GOD'S SAKE.

46:51.242 --> 46:52.508
YOU FEEL GOOD.
YOU FEEL BAD.

46:52.510 --> 46:53.976
YOU FEEL SAD.
YOU FEEL HAPPY.

46:53.978 --> 46:56.779
HEY, THERE'S ALWAYS A REASON TO
HAVE A CELEBRATION WITH

46:56.781 --> 46:57.613
A DRY MARTINI,

46:57.615 --> 46:59.615
BUT THE PROBLEM
WITH PEOPLE LIKE US

46:59.617 --> 47:01.250
IS THAT ONE MARTINI
LEADS TO ANOTHER MARTINI.

47:01.252 --> 47:02.785
IT LEADS TO A SCOTCH
ON THE ROCKS.

47:02.787 --> 47:04.320
IT LEADS TO A--IN MY CASE,

47:04.322 --> 47:08.324
THE CRYSTAL METHAMPHETAMINE,
AND THEN IT'S OVER.

47:08.326 --> 47:11.627
MANY OF YOU KNOW MY JOURNEY TO
SOBRIETY IN THESE LAST 11 YEARS,

47:11.629 --> 47:14.430
AND I'D BE LESS THAN HONEST
IF I WERE TO SAY TO YOU

47:14.432 --> 47:16.833
THAT I HAVEN'T WANTED TO HAVE A
DRINK MANY, MANY TIMES.

47:16.835 --> 47:17.934
I HAVE.

47:19.369 --> 47:21.671
BUT I THINK.

47:21.673 --> 47:25.741
I SIT DOWN, AND I THINK ABOUT
WHAT I'VE BEEN THROUGH...

47:27.978 --> 47:32.114
AND ALL MY FAMILY
AND MY FRIENDS

47:32.116 --> 47:34.483
AND THE PEOPLE
THAT I LOVE

47:34.485 --> 47:39.355
AND THAT STUCK BY ME
HAVE BEEN THROUGH.

47:39.357 --> 47:43.292
SO EVERY TIME I THINK
THAT I MIGHT BE SLIPPING...

48:11.521 --> 48:13.155
ARE YOU OKAY?

48:14.424 --> 48:16.559
YEAH, I'M FINE.

48:26.837 --> 48:28.804
[ HEAVY POUNDING ]

48:34.411 --> 48:36.412
[ POUNDING CONTINUES ]

48:58.235 --> 49:00.202
[ POUNDING CONTINUES ]

49:23.160 --> 49:25.161
[ POUNDING ON DOOR ]

49:34.471 --> 49:36.472
[ POUNDING STOPS ]

49:41.411 --> 49:43.279
[ KNOB RATTLING ]

49:43.281 --> 49:45.715
WHO'S THERE?!
WHO'S THERE?!

49:48.352 --> 49:49.385
[ RATTLING STOPS ]

49:58.195 --> 49:59.929
WHAT THE FUCK?

50:32.162 --> 50:33.562
FUCK.

50:57.888 --> 50:59.455
OKAY, BE STRONG.

51:02.392 --> 51:04.093
[ SNIFFS ]

51:45.936 --> 51:47.636
[ GASPS ]

51:58.315 --> 51:59.715
WHERE--OH.

51:59.717 --> 52:01.617
MICHAEL! MICHAEL!

52:01.619 --> 52:03.953
STOP IT! STOP IT!
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

52:03.955 --> 52:05.287
IT'S NOT IN MY HEAD.

52:05.289 --> 52:06.755
I THOUGHT
WE WERE PAST THIS.

52:06.757 --> 52:08.791
I SAW HER.
I SAW IT AGAIN.

52:08.793 --> 52:09.825
A-AND SOMETHING
HAPPENED HERE.

52:09.827 --> 52:12.628
AH, FUCK.
AND--AND--AND--

52:12.630 --> 52:14.063
MAYBE IT'S THE HOUSE.
MAYBE IT WANTS TO--

52:14.065 --> 52:15.131
I THOUGHT
WE WERE PAST THIS.

52:15.133 --> 52:16.398
MAYBE IT WANTS US
TO LEAVE.

52:16.400 --> 52:17.633
MAYBE THE REALTOR
LIED TO US.

52:17.635 --> 52:19.068
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?
YOU KNOW,

52:19.070 --> 52:20.970
SOMETHING SHE'S NOT TELLING US,
YOU KNOW?

52:20.972 --> 52:22.438
BECAUSE YOU KNOW
WHO LIVED HERE?

52:22.440 --> 52:24.140
I DON'T KNOW WHO--
WHO LIVED HERE

52:24.142 --> 52:25.307
BEFORE US,
AND MAYBE--

52:25.309 --> 52:26.642
WHY DID THEY LEAVE,
YOU KNOW?

52:26.644 --> 52:28.010
WHY DID THEY
HAVE TO GO?

52:28.012 --> 52:29.512
YOU ARE INSANE!
THESE PEOPLE--

52:29.514 --> 52:31.313
THESE PEOPLE, THESE THINGS,
THEY WANT US TO KNOW.

52:31.315 --> 52:32.748
THEY WANT US TO KNOW
WHAT'S GOING ON.

52:32.750 --> 52:33.983
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

52:33.985 --> 52:35.417
DO YOU KNOW WHO LIVED
HERE BEFORE US?

52:35.419 --> 52:37.253
I DON'T KNOW WHY THEY
CHOSE ME, BUT THEY DID,

52:37.255 --> 52:39.355
AND--
YOU DRANK?

52:39.357 --> 52:40.689
UH, FUCK.
YOU DRANK?

52:40.691 --> 52:41.991
I'M NOT GONNA
GIVE THEM THE HOUSE.

52:41.993 --> 52:43.125
I'M NOT GONNA--
YOU FUCKING DRANK?

52:43.127 --> 52:44.059
I'M NOT GONNA LEAVE.

52:45.328 --> 52:46.595
THAT'S NOT
WHAT'S IMPORTANT.

52:46.597 --> 52:48.030
YOU'RE SAYING
YOU NEVER DRANK!

52:48.032 --> 52:49.365
THAT'S NOT
WHAT'S IMPORTANT!

52:49.367 --> 52:51.133
FUCKING ASSHOLE.
LISTEN TO ME! LISTEN.

52:51.135 --> 52:52.601
I'M JUST TRYING
TO PROTECT YOU.

52:52.603 --> 52:54.003
FROM WHAT?
THE BOGEYMAN

52:54.005 --> 52:55.271
THAT'S TRYING
TO GET US?

52:55.273 --> 52:56.705
ALL OF
THE SECRET MESSAGES

52:56.707 --> 52:58.440
THAT ARE HIDDEN
IN THE PHONE CALLS?

52:59.876 --> 53:02.011
I'VE TRIED EVERYTHING
I CAN DO TO HELP YOU.

53:02.013 --> 53:03.012
I'M DONE.

53:04.181 --> 53:06.348
NO. NO.

53:06.350 --> 53:09.218
KATHERINE, I NEED YOU
TO BELIEVE ME.

53:09.220 --> 53:11.720
I'LL COME BACK TO GET THE REST
OF MY STUFF WHEN YOU'RE GONE.

53:11.722 --> 53:13.122
NO!

53:13.124 --> 53:15.558
[ ALARM CHIRPS ]

53:18.395 --> 53:19.395
[ CRYING ]

53:19.397 --> 53:21.430
[ WARNING TONE BEEPING ]

53:23.700 --> 53:25.568
[ TONE STOPS ]

53:38.081 --> 53:40.749
WELL, I'M SORRY, MA'AM.
I DIDN'T MEAN TO SCARE YOU.

53:42.018 --> 53:43.219
IT'S OKAY.

53:43.221 --> 53:44.753
WELL, I TRIED CALLING,

53:44.755 --> 53:47.256
BUT IT SEEMS YOU'RE
NOT ANSWERING YOUR PHONES.

53:47.258 --> 53:48.724
SORRY ABOUT THAT.

53:48.726 --> 53:50.192
AH, IT'S NO PROBLEM.

53:50.194 --> 53:52.928
WE GOT SOME INFORMATION BACK
ON THOSE PRIVATE CALLS.

53:52.930 --> 53:55.064
NOW, YOU SAY
THE PHONE WAS UNPLUGGED,

53:55.066 --> 53:56.599
BUT IT WAS
STILL RINGING?

53:56.601 --> 53:58.367
NO, THAT WAS A MISTAKE.

53:58.369 --> 53:59.535
[ CHUCKLES ]

53:59.537 --> 54:01.203
THOUGHT THAT SOUNDED
A LITTLE CRAZY.

54:01.205 --> 54:04.039
EVEN THOUGH WHAT WE FOUND
WAS A LITTLE CRAZY IN ITSELF.

54:04.041 --> 54:06.008
WHAT DO YOU MEAN?

54:06.010 --> 54:08.444
WELL, NORMALLY WE CAN EASILY
TRACE THESE TYPES OF CALLS,

54:08.446 --> 54:10.145
BECAUSE ALL NUMBERS, INCLUDING
PRIVATE ONES, HAVE A

54:10.147 --> 54:14.917
WHAT WAS WEIRD WAS EVERY TIME WE
TRIED ONE OF YOUR CALLS,

54:14.919 --> 54:16.418
OUR SYSTEMS CRASHED.

54:16.420 --> 54:18.420
IT WORKED WITH
EVERY OTHER NUMBER WE TRIED,

54:18.422 --> 54:20.623
BUT YOURS KEPT CAUSING
OUR EQUIPMENT TO FAIL.

54:22.692 --> 54:24.827
THAT'S WEIRD.

